{{vgname|零～zero～|ja=零〜zero〜|na=Fatal Frame|eu=Project Zero}}是发行于[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]和[[Xbox|Xbox]]的[[心理恐怖|心理恐怖]]电子游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/fatal-frame/related/release/platform/ps2/|title=Fatal Frame Release Summary|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=29 July 2012|archive-date=2013-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929115827/http://www.gamespot.com/fatal-frame/related/release/platform/ps2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[零系列|零系列]]的第一作。Xbox版在日本称为“Fatal Frame -零 Special Edition-”，加入了新结局，更多服装，新的游戏模式和更困难的设置{{citation needed|time=2014-09-05T17:14:09+00:00}}。游戏作为PlayStation 2 Classic，2013年为北美[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]的[[PlayStation_Network|PlayStation Network]]服务发行<ref name="psn_page">{{cite web |url=http://us.playstation.com/games/fatal-frame-ps3.html |title=Fatal Frame® Game | PS3™ - PlayStation® |publisher=Us.playstation.com |date=2013-04-09 |accessdate=2013-06-13 |archive-date=2014-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140528091730/http://us.playstation.com/games/fatal-frame-ps3.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2013/04/09/playstation-store-update-286/ |title=PlayStation Store Update – PlayStation.Blog |publisher=Blog.us.playstation.com |date=2013-04-09 |accessdate=2013-05-02 |archive-date=2020-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521104959/https://blog.us.playstation.com/2013/04/09/playstation-store-update-286/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

